select "suppliers"."company_name", COUNT(products.id) as products_count from "suppliers" left join "products" on "products"."supplier_id" = "suppliers"."id" where "suppliers"."company_id" = 1 group by "suppliers"."id", "suppliers"."company_name" order by "products_count" desc limit 5

select "suppliers"."company_name", SUM(products.stock * products.purchase_price) as total_value, COUNT(products.id) as products_count from "suppliers" left join "products" on "suppliers"."id" = "products"."supplier_id" where "suppliers"."company_id" = 1 group by "suppliers"."id", "suppliers"."company_name" order by "total_value" desc

select "p"."name", COUNT(sd.id) as times_sold, SUM(sd.quantity) as total_quantity, "p"."sale_price", SUM(sd.quantity * p.sale_price) as total_revenue from "sale_details" as "sd" inner join "products" as "p" on "sd"."product_id" = "p"."id" inner join "sales" as "s" on "sd"."sale_id" = "s"."id" where "s"."company_id" = 1 group by "p"."id", "p"."name", "p"."sale_price" order by "total_quantity" desc limit 10

select "c"."name", SUM(s.total_price) as total_spent, COUNT(DISTINCT sd.product_id) as unique_products, SUM(sd.quantity) as total_products from "sales" as "s" inner join "customers" as "c" on "s"."customer_id" = "c"."id" inner join "sale_details" as "sd" on "s"."id" = "sd"."sale_id" where "s"."company_id" = 1 group by "c"."id", "c"."name" order by "total_spent" desc limit 5

select COALESCE(cat.name, 'Sin Categoría') as name, COUNT(sd.id) as total_sales, SUM(sd.quantity) as total_quantity, SUM(sd.quantity * p.sale_price) as total_revenue from "sale_details" as "sd" inner join "products" as "p" on "sd"."product_id" = "p"."id" left join "categories" as "cat" on "p"."category_id" = "cat"."id" inner join "sales" as "s" on "sd"."sale_id" = "s"."id" where "s"."company_id" = 1 group by "cat"."id", "cat"."name" order by "total_revenue" desc
